Question: Jiangsu Tenwei Electronic Co., Ltd. CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Jiangsu Tenwei Electronic Co., Ltd.

CES 2024 Product Highlight:

- Supplier of 3C digital accessories and mobile solutions
- Product range includes basic charger, QC3.0 charger, PD charger, power bank, wireless charger, power stripe, wall/car charger
- Headquartered in Nanjing, China with R&D and operation centers in Shenzhen, Huaian, Nanjing, and Vietnam
- Three brands: "Tenwei," "Wishinkle," and "Chanki" catering to different consumer requirements
- Distribution partners in over 30 countries, popular in Europe and US
- New factory in Ho Chi Minh, Vietnam for competitive pricing
- Emphasis on good quality materials and strict high-quality management

For product inquiries or distributor partnership, please contact the company.
